# Design System for Beauty by Raquel Nicole

## Color Palette
```css
:root {
  --color-primary: #F9E6E6;    /* Blush Pink */
  --color-secondary: #F3D7C6;  /* Warm Beige */
  --color-accent: #C2876C;     /* Rose Gold */
  --color-text: #3C3C3C;       /* Charcoal Gray */
  --color-bg: #FFF8F5;         /* Off-White */
}
```

## Typography System
- **Headers:** Playfair Display (serif)
  - H1: 48px/1.2, Bold (Mobile: 32px)
  - H2: 36px/1.3, Semi-bold
  - H3: 28px/1.4, Regular
- **Body:** Lato (sans-serif)
  - Paragraphs: 16px/1.6, Regular (Mobile: 14px)
  - Small Text: 12px, Medium
- **Buttons:** Montserrat, 14px, Bold, Uppercase

## Component Standards
- **Navigation:** Sticky header with logo (left), menu (center), Book Now CTA (right)
- **Buttons:** Primary (filled blush pink), Secondary (outline), min 48px height
- **Cards:** Service cards with image, title, description, price, CTA
- **Forms:** Floating labels, validation states (success/error)
- **Modals:** Slide-in confirmations, toast notifications

## Layout System
- **Grid:** 12-column desktop, 4-column mobile
- **Gutters:** 24px desktop, 16px mobile
- **Max Width:** 1200px
- **Spacing:** XS(4px), S(8px), M(16px), L(24px), XL(48px)

## Interaction Guidelines
- **Hover Effects:** Subtle background tone changes and elevation
- **Transitions:** Smooth 0.3s fade for modals and galleries
- **Loading States:** Skeleton loaders for dynamic content
- **Micro-interactions:** Booking button pulse on homepage

## Accessibility Requirements
- **Contrast:** WCAG AA compliance for all text/background combinations
- **Focus States:** Visible focus indicators for keyboard navigation
- **Alt Text:** Descriptive alt text for all images
- **ARIA Labels:** Proper labeling for interactive elements

## Mobile-First Approach
- Responsive breakpoints: Mobile (<768px), Tablet (768-1024px), Desktop (>1024px)
- Touch-friendly button sizes (min 44px)
- Optimized typography scaling
- Simplified navigation for mobile users

## Brand Integration
- Logo placement in header and footer
- Consistent use of brand colors and typography
- Professional imagery with soft lighting and neutral backgrounds
- Emphasis on natural beauty and personalized care messaging
